---
import avatarPhoto from '../assets/avatar.JPG';
import React from 'react';
---
<div id="container">
	<main class="h-full flex justify-center">
		<section id="hero" class="flex items-center flex-col justify-center">
			<div class="">
				<img src={avatarPhoto.src} width="100" height="100" class="rounded-full sm:w-70 sm:h-70 md:w-50 md:h-50" alt="avatar"/>
			</div>
			<div class="pt-5">
				<h1 class="font-extrabold text-2xl md:text-3xl ">Hi, I'm Du Van Nguyen!</h1>
			</div>
			<span class="sm:text-sm md:text-xl pt-3 px-5 md:mr-30 md:ml-30 lg:mr-60 lg:ml-60">
					I am currently a third year student at Swinburne University of
                    Technology, studying <mark class="highlightword text-[1rem] px-1 py-1/5 rounded">Computer Science</mark> with a major in <mark class="highlightword text-[1rem] px-1 py-1/5 rounded">Software
                    Development</mark>. Additionally, I'm also a <mark class="highlightword text-[1rem] px-1 py-1/5 rounded"> game developer intern</mark> at Education Network
                    Group. Given my <mark class="highlightword text-[1rem] px-1 py-1/5 rounded">passion for problem-solving</mark>, I have made it my goal to become a software developer. Despite
                    being new to the industry, I am always <mark class="highlightword text-[1rem] px-1 py-1/5 rounded">eager to learn more and improve
                    my skills</mark> as I believe it is important to quickly adapt in this
                    forever changing world of technology.
			</span>
		</section>
	</main>
</div>

<style>
	#container {
		height: 80%;
	}
</style>
